# Signal Noise — Caddy vhost SNIPPET (append only).
#
# ⚠️  The live /etc/caddy/Caddyfile on the VPS is a MULTI-SITE file that already
#     serves other vhosts (e.g. scuffedcrew.no -> :3100, Paperclip itself).
#     NEVER overwrite it. scripts/provision.sh APPENDS the block below (after a
#     `caddy validate`) only if it is not already present.
#
# Live block currently in place (auto-TLS via the existing Caddy + Let's Encrypt):

news.scuffedcrew.no {
    encode zstd gzip
    reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:8888
}

